<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-the-near-future">in the (near) future</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在 (不久的) 将来</strong></h4>
<p>soon：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No one can tell what will happen in the future.
没人能说准将来会发生什么事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The film market may witness a slowdown in the near future.
在不久的将来电影市场也许会萎缩。</p><footer>2016 江苏书面表达</footer></div></div>